--- Switchblade / Astroblast ---

Switchblade has finished repairing Dead-End's side circuitry, and 
begins on the arm. He shakes his head.

Astroblast comes into sight of the CF and the Element. He arms 
his twin laser cannons and lets eight bright purple blasts ripple 
across the battle field at the Element. "Megatron, I have arrived 
what are my orders?"
